{"id":28466,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":8,"day":25}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"灯塔","column":"问答栏:,大众信箱","genre":"","count":"93","ytitle":"","mtitle":"捐过了","ftitle":"","authors":["沈杰"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"寡捐者:先生!请你捐几个钱，救济救济难民，功德无量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富翁:捐过了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"募捐者:先生!请问捐款送到那一个机关里去的?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富翁:这不是收条吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"募捐者:唔!原来是难民奖券。"}]}